Recommended Usage

Check the Daily chart and confirm that the market is moving sideways.

Switch to the 1-hour timeframe.

Apply the strategy to BTC or SOL.

Monitor performance and adjust parameters such as the percentage offsets if needed.
Release Notes
This strategy has been specifically optimized for Solana (SOL) on the 1H chart. This Stategy prioritizes Risk Managment over all, so you can use it on a fundet Account.

For the best results, it is recommended not to modify the code and simply use the settings defined at the top of the script. (Look at the Code under Settings:)

The parameters included there were carefully selected during the optimization process, and changing them may significantly affect the performance of the indicator.

If this indicator helps you generate profits, it would be greatly appreciated if you consider giving something back as a way of supporting the work behind it. Your support helps to continue developing and improving tools like this.
